desc.zh: 讷河市轨道交通系统线路图，建设于2050年，共有14条线路，连接城市内各大人流密集处和早晚高峰区域，包括学校和住宅区，车站命名基于现实
desc.en: The map of the rail transit system in Nehe City, built in 2050, consists of 14 lines that connect various densely populated areas and peak morning and evening rush hour zones within the city, including schools and residential areas. The station names are based on reality
